text: Edward Maw (15 June 1902 - 12 July 1991) was a British swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1991 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
